cqcontent-content-json.headline: Put your best foot forward.
cqcontent-content-json.editorialCopy: The Power Stride Tab Sock hugs your heel for stability where you need it most.
cqcontent-content-json.imageAltText: A man is outside putting on his running shoe while wearing the Power Stride Tab Sock.

cqcontent-content-json.heading: Socks for sweat, rest, and repeat.
cqcontent-content-json.imageAlt: A man is sitting in the grass outside pulling on the Power Stride Tab Sock.

cqcontent-content-json.headline: Your socks are specific.
cqcontent-content-json.editorialCopy: Whether you like them high, low, or no-show, our socks have 360° arch support, and Performaheel™ technology that keeps them in place.
cqcontent-content-json.imageAltText: Four single grey socks in different lengths.

cqcontent-content-json.headline: Socks that don't disappear.
cqcontent-content-json.editorialCopy: PerformaHeel™ technology. Active grip heel tab. 360° arch support. These socks are made for working out in—and yes, they really do stay on.
cqcontent-content-json.imageAltText: text: Zoomed in shot of person wearing white Power Stride No Show Socks.

properties.long-description: Men's training, yoga, and run gear built for the body in motion. Keep moving in technical fabrics engineered to handle some serious sweat. Free shipping + returns.
